Title: Red Cell
Plot: After a marine is murdered in the school campus the team discovers a possible suspect for his murder, but they are soon leaded back to zero point when they find the suspect murdered. Tim & Abby discover a trace to a ""Red Cell"" in the e-mails and the team believes that maybe the marine was involved in a serious game...
GuestStars: Jeff Wincott, Sherman Augustus, Brian Dietzen, Matt DeCaro, Jon Wellner, Judd Trichter, Kaj-Erik Eriksen, Billy Aaron Brown, Chase Ryan Jeffery
